Choose either the medicaments or the symtpoms view and search for single or multiple symptoms (separated by a dot (.)). In the medicaments view there is already made a repertoriasation (attention this is not reliable) and the medicaments with the most hits and the highest grade score are shown on top. Now you can select the grade of the symptoms (1-10) and after this you can make a real repertoriasation (by pressing on 'search symptoms' or 'search symptoms add'. If the last menu is seleted this search is added to the last search, otherwise a new search is made. By a long press on a symptoms a context menu is shown and you can reset the selection (all sub-symptoms are shown again) or make a search in the internet.